========================================================================
2. libengine_bridge.so
========================================================================
Size     : ~15 KB
Origin   : Regalia project — Engine JNI Bridge
License  : GNU General Public License v3 (GPL v3)
Copyright: (C) 2026 Regalia
           DroidFish-derived parts: (C) 2011-2014 Peter Österlund
Source   : src/main/cpp/engine_jni.cpp

This library provides the JNI bridge for loading and communicating with
the UCI chess engine (libstockfish.so) via dlopen()/dlsym() and pipe-based
I/O. It also includes native chmod and renice functionality derived from
DroidFish (nativeutil.cpp by Peter Österlund).

Full license text: LICENSE-GPL v3 (included in the lib folder)

