3. libstockfish.so
========================================================================
Size     : ~109 MB (arm64-v8a-dotprod build)
Origin   : Stockfish Chess Engine
License  : GNU General Public License v3 (GPL v3)
Copyright: (C) Tord Romstad, Marco Costalba, Joona Kiiski, Gary Linscott
           and the Stockfish contributors (see AUTHORS-stockfish)
Source   : https://github.com/official-stockfish/Stockfish

Stockfish is a free, open-source UCI chess engine. This build is
Stockfish 18 compiled for the arm64-v8a architecture with dotprod
extensions enabled.

Full license text: LICENSE-GPL v3 (included in the lib folder)
Full authors list : AUTHORS-stockfish (included in the lib folder)

